India’s CBI Probing Reliance Telecom Role in Swan Transfer Case

-- B y   P r a t a p   P a t n a i k
-- 
2011-09-29T10:14:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/india-s-cbi-probing-reliance-telecom-role-in-swan-transfer-case.html
India ’s federal investigators are
probing the role of Reliance Telecom Ltd. in the transfer of
Swan Telecom Pvt. to Mauritius-based Delphi Investments Ltd.,
K.K. Venugopal, a lawyer representing the  Central Bureau of
Investigation , told a two-judge panel headed by G.S. Singhvi in
 New Delhi  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
